title: Bucks, OBJ, Tom Brady, and the Patriots
itunes:title: Bucks, OBJ, Tom Brady, and the Patriots
description:
Colin explains why the Milwaukee Bucks are not a championship team, why Odell Beckham Jr. is a horrible fit in Cleveland, why the Tom Brady to the 49ers story is ridiculous, and why he still feels Brady will stay in New England. Guests include Ric Bucher, LaVar Ball, Tom Curran, and Bucky Brooks.
